/>\n用電如倒水<br />\n係清過PSP版又如何<br />\nPSP續航力高好多又無咁易過熱<br />\n<br />\n有人check過Switch打機時頂盡用十幾Watt電<br />\n如出1080p mon版<br />\n你可以預計到用多幾多Watt電<br />\n到時用電仲多過好多款Notebook<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n或者你等Sony或MS出部4K mon手提遊戲機比你玩啦<br />\n十年內應該出到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都應該有命等到"},{"pid":"002ce90976ac50d4f70e8a1fb45ca1480785d1af","tid":279524,"uid":34161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T16:55:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人類歷史上所有手提遊戲機出個時<br />\n個mon解像度都係低過同期好多手機</blockquote><br />\n好撚肯定 gameboy 出嗰陣啲手機連點陣 LCD 都未有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f8af2fe9ff62c66963b3a6b8ac2534a6404436","tid":279524,"uid":113914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T16:59:19.000Z","msg":"我仲想買添 睇黎可以唔買住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b927a5548768586d7631d1b0cdbe755389f614d7","tid":279524,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T17:09:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>三月中買<br />\n早排中左boot loop(開黎開去都係得版error)<br />\n換完機到依家一切正常<br />\n但70個鐘薩爾達冇左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無得backup save落sd card真係超on9</blockquote><br />\n當自己gameboy呀 <br />\nonline game play 就識收錢 cloud save 就唔識做</blockquote><br />\nonline未開始收錢喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2018年咪開始囉，但佢咁既硬件，咁少game，家庭遊戲機得720p，咁既條件都敢收online play錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身都覺得得閒玩下冇咩所謂，依家機錢都可以慳返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTV 1080p<br />\nhandheld 720p</blockquote><br />\n手機有2k,<br />\n三年前用緊果部都有1080p<br />\n<br />\nswitch 個硬件的確戇撚鳩喎"}]}